title: Grateful Dead Live at Kiel Auditorium on 1973-10-29
description:
Set I
Cold Rain & Snow
Beat It On Down The Line
Brown Eyed Women
Mexicali Blues
Don't Ease Me In

The Race Is On

El Paso
Eyes Of The World >

Set II

Comment
Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Keith Godchaux - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Donna Jean Godchaux - Vocals
